			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Any spells which were DRU/SHM/NEC/MAG are now DRU/SHM/NEC.
<br />

<br />
The system works something like this now:
<br />

<br />
2 types of traps/locks affected by casters: Magic and Cursed.
<br />

<br />
Druids, Shaman, Clerics, and Necros may detect/disarm cursed traps/locks.  Clerics outperform the others in this case.
<br />

<br />
Mages, Wizards, Necros, and Enchanters may detect/disarm magic traps/locks.  Wizards outperform the others in this case.
<br />

<br />
There are also mechanical traps/locks which Bards and Rogues may detect/disarm; Rogues performing better than Bards.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
