			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have noticed that many of the spells on Adventure Merchants may only have a couple of classes listed that can use that spell. I.E. Spirit of the Shrew at merchant A may only have DRU listed as a class, but at merchant B it has SHM listed. I think this is probably more of what people are seeing - there are different scrolls that scribe the same spell.
<br />

<br />
I believe this was done so that different classes would pay different points for the same spell. So that hybrids would pay more points for spells the pure caster got long ago for cheap.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=99869" target="_blank">Perelandra Eldil - Arch Convoker</a> 
<br />
Gelil - Oracle
